RAADS-R QUESTIONNAIRE CONTENT
==============================

The questionnaire item text, scoring methodology, and domain definitions in
src/data/dataset.json are derived from:

    Ritvo, R.A., Ritvo, E.R., Guthrie, D., Ritvo, M.J., Hufnagel, D.H.,
    Turner, W., Mcmahon, W.M., Aman, J., Ghahramani, P., & Eloff, J. (2011).
    The Ritvo Autism Asperger Diagnostic Scale-Revised (RAADS-R): A Scale to
    Assist the Diagnosis of Autism Spectrum Disorder in Adults: An International
    Validation Study. Journal of Autism and Developmental Disorders, 41(8),
    1076-1085. https://doi.org/10.1007/s10803-010-1133-5

This content is used under CC BY-NC from the original open access publication.
